cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with a semi-supervised learning approach for images based on in-painting using an adversarial loss. This involves the use of a generator and discriminator network, which are commonly used in computer vision and machine learning, falling under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
